{"tid":372191,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三國時代魏蜀吳語言其實相通唔通？","createTime":"2017-08-24T07:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T06:19:12.000Z","uid":81234,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b37596e6fa93ea809da4eff236dd6bf27bbec2b","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"各國士兵將領講唔到語言？<br />\n定都係講同一種"},{"pid":"b691c6122b2362152a1a6670c14233da035e5275","tid":372191,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:29:32.000Z","msg":"有古代旗語，例如呢個<br />\n「聞雷鼓音，舉白幢絳旗，大小船進戰，不進者斬。」《北堂書鈔》卷一百二十。〉"},{"pid":"127f270bf8dc80df4915dcb90caa3f2deb8db524","tid":372191,"uid":119223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"搭單一問其實同而家粵語，普通話相差幾遠？"},{"pid":"06577aec9e6de2314d080c6a2fcc5ee59f18b749","tid":372191,"uid":134834,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"有三國之前是漢<br />\n漢朝無統一語言點溝通<br />\n應該係話秦果期已經統一晒啦<br />\n除左小數民族"},{"pid":"d7365afe346674e6ae00da93db4f713e887a334c","tid":372191,"uid":93266,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:34:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsVw9iyq59zo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=89e250b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語"},{"pid":"ca3ccc0fafe19e353e7cab91b14c4c83d085a4bd","tid":372191,"uid":93266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各國士兵將領講唔到語言？<br />\n定都係講同一種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做官既要識官話 , 帶兵既要識土話同地方話"},{"pid":"ce9020b0783a7790fb3f5910122ac4feab3f56b1","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>各國士兵將領講唔到語言？<br />\n定都係講同一種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做官既要識官話 , 帶兵既要識土話同地方話</blockquote><br />\n成日有投敵果d咁點算"},{"pid":"32fce98ed3f0575bdecce579983ccda168c28d1a","tid":372191,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>各國士兵將領講唔到語言？<br />\n定都係講同一種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做官既要識官話 , 帶兵既要識土話同地方話</blockquote><br />\n成日有投敵果d咁點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無問題呀 , 總會有個鄉里係左近"},{"pid":"874f1b1e4b142eb340ab3aaac5d135a1c6d40e6f","tid":372191,"uid":5502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有三國之前是漢<br />\n漢朝無統一語言點溝通<br />\n應該係話秦果期已經統一晒啦<br />\n除左小數民族</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇統一語言，得統一文字"},{"pid":"9a4e3cd7aa187d49b39f3e819af4ee29f4d75982","tid":372191,"uid":86530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有三國之前是漢<br />\n漢朝無統一語言點溝通<br />\n應該係話秦果期已經統一晒啦<br />\n除左小數民族</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇統一語言，得統一文字</blockquote><br />\n終國過咗咁耐都統一唔到普通話<br />\n成堆人只係識講鄉下話<br />\n更加唔好講用飛鴿傳書嘅古代"},{"pid":"cdbccac5639f42a80fef1cffe87e2aaf314338da","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"我就唔信古代會通得晒<br />\n依家上海同重慶同香港都各有方言啦"},{"pid":"98b1f84626badd7c7e3021e46e474746c1e9cf13","tid":372191,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"現代係浙江一帶方言 吳語最似古語"},{"pid":"8cda5abc2c7228fd4b3c2a1f0e2577de4cb3700e","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsVw9iyq59zo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=89e250b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語</blockquote><br />\n難我巴打聽過中古漢語 抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係喺漢語語言學 周代至南北朝嘅漢語都劃分做上古漢語<br />\n所以三國時代講嘅語言 應該係上古漢語"},{"pid":"4c08a182c7039bec68f502162df78a75ffd6d4f7","tid":372191,"uid":68290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bqt3_02lxGo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBqt3_02lxGo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d79b5765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bqt3_02lxGo</a><br />\n呢啲叫上古漢語？其實係泰文咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8ff416cbba21ec8fc700c95d28ffe9a84e9121","tid":372191,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5da76f1cdea930fa7d5f668e9d7623c4ad3c9e66","tid":372191,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"你以為漢朝版圖好大咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漢族基本上都同一語系"},{"pid":"7e0fe675dc6e059f5f0e30c8211b532a9fc2eb35","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單一問其實同而家粵語，普通話相差幾遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國時代講嘅係上古漢語<br />\n再準確啲 應該係晚期上古漢語<br />\n<br />\n同現代粵普嘅差異非常大 我喺咁椅講兩個<br />\n<br />\n古無輕唇音<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個特徵喺早期中古漢語都仲存在<br />\n具體嚟講 即係冇f(清唇齒擦音)或/及v(濁唇齒擦音)呢兩個音<br />\nf v 係後起嘅 源於p(清不送氣雙唇塞音) pʰ(清送氣雙唇塞音) b(濁雙唇塞音)<br />\n呢D音<br />\n<br />\n例證有好多 舉一個例: 《論語》﹕「且在邦城之中矣」 《釋文》注﹕「邦或作封」意思係邦同封差唔多音<br />\n<br />\n古無舌上音<br />\n<br />\n意思係指上古漢語冇切韻所講嘅「知徹澄」聲母<br />\n箇中嘅野好技術性 唔多講<br />\n簡單而言 即係 端知，透徹，定澄  呢三組字 <br />\n每一組入面嗰兩個字嘅聲母 喺上古漢語都係一樣嘅<br />\n用國際音標去標音 端知係t(清不送氣齒齦塞音) 透徹係tʰ(清送氣齒齦塞音)，定澄係d(濁齒齦塞音)<br />\n<br />\n例證可以喺閩方言度搵倒 舉一個算係出名嘅例子<br />\n茶喺呢個世界嘅語言多數都係讀做 類似查或者&quot;tee/tea&quot;呢兩種音<br />\n後音源於閩語 寫出嚟其實都係茶 但係因為佢保留咗「無舌上音」呢個特徵<br />\n所以個聲母係t(清不送氣齒齦塞音)"},{"pid":"c5333e05bc0e2ad70d08bae59aee442916a54a9d","tid":372191,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"吳國人講嘅語言可能聽得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1bbcd484f4b63a2f1027a0b35ef59ad2e4b26a","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bqt3_02lxGo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBqt3_02lxGo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d79b5765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bqt3_02lxGo</a><br />\n呢啲叫上古漢語？其實係泰文咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實相比起中古漢語<br />\n上古漢語嘅音系 爭議性比較大<br />\n所以呢個版本未必反映真實嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n當然有幾個位都冇咩學者反對<br />\n例:複輔音kr gr等等應該冇擬構錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(不過&quot;r&quot;嘅音值未必係片中用嘅顫音 可能係個閃音)"},{"pid":"ee97e2a9899addb3a1b9e8724532abb155cd25bd","tid":372191,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"上面貼果兩條link, 將進酒都話押押地韻<br />\n下面果條真心唔知讀緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b323758904d0bb0db4ab0696eb00e4122a06369","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsVw9iyq59zo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=89e250b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語</blockquote><br />\n都唔押韻嘅</blockquote><br />\n點解咁講??"},{"pid":"4aa350e9f7fc15378f0e0be3a260ae0ce1851b39","tid":372191,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:08:00.000Z","msg":"普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！"},{"pid":"21304342f8aa7b78fa28ec74100e3c80206c650c","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！</blockquote><br />\n介唔介意講吓你回覆緊邊個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6118e326050687938f3303703fb6558f41651235","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！</blockquote><br />\n我都嚇左嚇<br />\n我有用普通話做例咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9872aa65074cc35d109c43a289dd6854d42002de","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！</blockquote><br />\n我都嚇左嚇<br />\n我有用普通話做例咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「你唔好羅英語，法語來比！」<br />\n我最睇唔明呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f56b4d43c7245849ee176c09a1101b76f2c833b","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！</blockquote><br />\n其實在座所有人都知普通話係北佬語<br />\n你以為得你一個知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006bb531aed89812094479d952ca2a637047efa9","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！</blockquote><br />\n我都嚇左嚇<br />\n我有用普通話做例咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係播 樓主 我發現我好似冇回覆過你成個post嘅問題<br />\n魏吳應該溝通唔倒 因為西晉末年嘅永嘉之亂令好多北人去咗吳地<br />\n佢地話(當時嘅)吳語同佢地嘅話有明顯差異<br />\n只係爭幾廿年 我諗三國時嘅魏吳都係溝通唔倒<br />\n<br />\n蜀唔清楚 我去研究吓先"},{"pid":"5cbf740f5802cb1cb82b135ddd81ac3442084a49","tid":372191,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"蜀人應該同魏吳啲人傾唔到，因為蜀地有自己嘅語言系統(古蜀語)，而且蜀人係有強烈嘅本土意識係度，會好強調本土語言"},{"pid":"409eb43675096dc4150e1b777b7175e19c06aff6","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蜀人應該同魏吳啲人傾唔到，因為蜀地有自己嘅語言系統(古蜀語)，而且蜀人係有強烈嘅本土意識係度，會好強調本土語言</blockquote><br />\n吳既山越人應該都係用粵語"},{"pid":"7fa1c4aadb49829b3fe12fae71c27661230cbb7c","tid":372191,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"我諗好多人都同時識幾種方言，好似歐洲將領通常會識自己語言同拉丁/希臘/波斯文"},{"pid":"ad25f08e08e4c7dec79da53e7e948ee316232c34","tid":372191,"uid":81234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗好多人都同時識幾種方言，好似歐洲將領通常會識自己語言同拉丁/希臘/波斯文</blockquote><br />\n依家2017年有Google有internet <br />\n醒目既香港人多數都係識普通話同英文 仲大部份唔係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前仲要飯都冇得食書都冇得讀應該唔會咁勁掛"},{"pid":"541d7b043f99fafa7b5784533c4f5e7723114492","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蜀人應該同魏吳啲人傾唔到，因為蜀地有自己嘅語言系統(古蜀語)，而且蜀人係有強烈嘅本土意識係度，會好強調本土語言</blockquote><br />\n吳既山越人應該都係用粵語</blockquote><br />\n山越應該唔係講漢語架喎"},{"pid":"18d93e96d6fae7c497cbf90becabbbf9a699afb0","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗好多人都同時識幾種方言，好似歐洲<span style=\"color: red;\">將領</span>通常會識自己語言同拉丁/希臘/波斯文</blockquote><br />\n重點"},{"pid":"69a155841ab0132d848fd5d2a64bb9abf0b3156d","tid":372191,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>普通話都唔係中原本土語言，是北方草原民族契丹人的「胡語」，你唔好羅英語，法語來比！<br />\n係都羅客家話，上海話，閩南話來比啦！</blockquote><br />\n我都嚇左嚇<br />\n我有用普通話做例咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「你唔好羅英語，法語來比！」<br />\n我最睇唔明呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條友可能take左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036e772d7e04c7268a17370182a1f787393a1197","tid":372191,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsVw9iyq59zo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=89e250b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個唔準確，參考就得"},{"pid":"34b4888c1a42f38574e8ff3d6cea66c83d7f0cfc","tid":372191,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有三國之前是漢<br />\n漢朝無統一語言點溝通<br />\n應該係話秦果期已經統一晒啦<br />\n除左小數民族</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇統一語言，得統一文字</blockquote><br />\n終國過咗咁耐都統一唔到普通話<br />\n成堆人只係識講鄉下話<br />\n更加唔好講用飛鴿傳書嘅古代</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有鄉下話先好，個個淨識講一種語言，共匪至易操控"},{"pid":"8c061e90bcb0fbd45ae9fdb239b9bd11e01e8ba3","tid":372191,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"漢高祖乃楚人"},{"pid":"cedea86db8f64290ba7d61aac5d39fb0be7f8bb9","tid":372191,"uid":49754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n其實啲人靠咩方法搵返古漢語既讀音係點?"},{"pid":"bcf0c9cb6e8ab2c9ba095bbbcb1391ff4ef126fe","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問<br />\n其實啲人靠咩方法搵返古漢語既讀音係點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好問題!<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語同近古漢語就主要靠韻書同韻圖<br />\n呢啲書本身係關於中古同近古音嘅音系分析<br />\n所以呢啲書對了解當時嘅音系好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n但係上古漢語就唔同 冇呢種書<br />\n所以我地後人要靠詩嘅韻腳、形聲字、雙聲字、假借字等等資料<br />\n去研究上古漢語嘅音系"},{"pid":"e6d97a4711d782c1839fa6498cd978e179aeb329","tid":372191,"uid":6134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dcb835209a068ea411b6e87fb87914e60a1303","tid":372191,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蜀人應該同魏吳啲人傾唔到，因為蜀地有自己嘅語言系統(古蜀語)，而且蜀人係有強烈嘅本土意識係度，會好強調本土語言</blockquote><br />\n蜀人好多本身係外地人"},{"pid":"7a73c9a7ed75d9fa094ec891beb75fd5e81c5296","tid":372191,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsVw9iyq59zo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=89e250b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語</blockquote><br />\n根本客家話黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdec3408267e2ce2ca73e713024b97ef262c43d4","tid":372191,"uid":15921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗好多人都同時識幾種方言，好似歐洲將領通常會識自己語言同拉丁/希臘/波斯文</blockquote><br />\n依家2017年有Google有internet <br />\n醒目既香港人多數都係識普通話同英文 仲大部份唔係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前仲要飯都冇得食書都冇得讀應該唔會咁勁掛</blockquote><br />\n說話又唔係咁講，我老母都識客家話廣東話同學佬<br />\n鄉下人要語言，應該唔難<br />\n問題係佢有冇需要"},{"pid":"723a4d2d5ace2fdc088681c40573e2742569bd98","tid":372191,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsVw9iyq59zo&d=9aZEzKY2dc2u1LkVW86v9ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=89e250b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVw9iyq59zo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中古漢語</blockquote><br />\n根本客家話黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係幾似"},{"pid":"ba7415631e2ec875d52343f19583a39cd786fe0a","tid":372191,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現代係浙江一帶方言 吳語最似古語</blockquote><br />\n東南地區啲方言最似古漢語"},{"pid":"fff79fb35ba1285da1bbc2a983de5fd1c2e96348","tid":372191,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"古漢語真係冇乜f音，閩南話，泡語，日語(非外來詞)都係"},{"pid":"bb7019922c063e7813ece8753d0e5648a18266da","tid":372191,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蜀人應該同魏吳啲人傾唔到，因為蜀地有自己嘅語言系統(古蜀語)，而且蜀人係有強烈嘅本土意識係度，會好強調本土語言</blockquote><br />\n始祖巴蜀人已經俾秦同南越先後收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34760b2f02180d6b55682cf81bcfd35e6e777ea5","tid":372191,"uid":79959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"文言文應該係用來記錄，唔係用來講，川語似普，魏語似普，吳語唔似普"},{"pid":"58f5e0da77eefec97b5f1eb98811fea89cac6fd9","tid":372191,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文言文應該係用來記錄，唔係用來講，川語似普，魏語似普，吳語唔似普</blockquote><br />\n咁講又啱唔曬 文言文反映嘅係春秋戰國嘅漢語 即使冇十成 都應該接近"},{"pid":"5a5087e01d7606622f4ed4b63f488e71a3081fbb","tid":372191,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蜀人應該同魏吳啲人傾唔到，因為蜀地有自己嘅語言系統(古蜀語)，而且蜀人係有強烈嘅本土意識係度，會好強調本土語言</blockquote><br />\n始祖巴蜀人已經俾秦同南越先後收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南越領土無咁廣"}]}